+//! MicroLoRA: Rank-2 Low-Rank Adaptation with <100us latency
+//!
+//! Implements the core LoRA algorithm: output = input + alpha * (input @ A @ B)
+//! where A: [d x 2] and B: [2 x d] for rank-2 adaptation.
